flowchart TD
  Start[Open app] --> Login[Log in]
  Login --> JoinGuild[Join local guild]
  JoinGuild --> FindGiver[Find quest giver]
  FindGiver --> CreateQuest[Create quest]
  CreateQuest --> FillForm[Fill form title description reward conditions acceptance delivery]
  FillForm --> MapLoc[Set map location]
  FillForm --> SelectRoles[Select roles party A party B notary lawyer mediator]
  FillForm --> LinkLaw[Link to constitution and applicable law]
  LinkLaw --> Register[Register quest in chancellery]
  Register --> Ledger[Ledger store headers versions signatures CID]
  Register --> Escrow[Fund escrow by party A]
  Escrow --> Execute[Execute work by party B]
  Execute --> Submit[Submit proofs and_delivery]
  Submit --> GuildReview[Guild review and acceptance quorum]
  GuildReview --> Release[Release payment]
  GuildReview --> Court[Court decision if_dispute]
  Court --> Release
  Release --> MediatorFee[Pay mediator fee one percent]
  Release --> Tax[Pay tax ten percent to treasury via guild]
  Release --> Performer[Pay net amount to party B]
  Performer --> Close[Close quest and_archive]
  MapLoc --> Register
  JoinGuild --> NotaryLawyer[Guild hosts notary and lawyer]
  NotaryLawyer --> GuildReview